sentences.chinese: 马的步幅比其他几种跑步较短，但却不失弹性与节奏。

sentences.english: Changshan archipelago is rich in resources, and the development of coastal economy is very fast.

sentences.english: Unlike lions or cheetahs, leopards are secretive, solitary cats.

sentences.english: Non -stress test has a higher clinical value in foretelling perinatal prognosis ofp olyhydramnios.
